.SH "STANDARD OPTIONS"
\fB\-background\fR	\fB\-highlightbackground\fR	\fB\-insertontime\fR	\fB\-selectborderwidth\fR
\fB\-borderwidth\fR	\fB\-highlightcolor\fR	\fB\-insertwidth\fR	\fB\-selectforeground\fR
